title: SetUpCamp
---
//Will need to access logic for player location in-game.
//will play upon player attempting to set up tent.
<<if $MakeCamp == true>>
    <<stop>>  // End the node immediately if it has already played
<<else>>
<<jump SetUpCampTree>>
<<endif>>
